{"tid":528351,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"我想收番以後唔再聯絡個句:-(","createTime":"2018-01-13T16:36:24.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-14T07:32:17.000Z","uid":134006,"like":2,"dislike":16,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"5d3dd314344d94e1ad77858c6d042371efd05430","tid":528351,"uid":134006,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-13T16:36:24.000Z","msg":"我想收番以後唔再聯絡個句<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n覺得自己好幼稚 好想再見面既我可以成熟啲<br />\n佢雖然只係識左你一陣 但諗番佢比你既快樂<br />\n可能遠遠不及我比你既<br />\n所以都冇理由去嬲或唔開心<br />\n<br />\n成日係度諗 如果平安夜你有守約定咁陪我而唔係佢<br />\n故事會唔會唔同哂<br />\n<br />\n但無論如何 你講過要細水長流<br />\n好難 但希望我用時間證明比你睇我做到<br />\n我剩係會鐘意你一個<br />\n<br />\n如果再見 准我以一個已成長的自己帶領你<br />\n記得你成日話我唔成熟<br />\n不過短期內都係唔好見<br />\n<br />\n好想收番以後唔再聯絡個句<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n你應該知我係邊個 曾經一齊共用連登帳號既<br />\n希望你收到 _ _ _.is.on9<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />上<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">留言最好正面少少 現實生活聽夠多負面野 我仲未想放棄你啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span>"},{"pid":"f63a63eba358b9f790328f4cbc30ff193ff1e805","tid":528351,"uid":30836,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-13T16:40:25.000Z","msg":"呢個唔掂咪下一個"},{"pid":"48b4131b7d78a208b846f415cdc312152049876c","tid":528351,"uid":14476,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-13T16:42:02.000Z","msg":"幼稚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"58929cc41f7119f4ba91e31b362848f101ad88c0","tid":528351,"uid":134006,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"f63a63eba358b9f790328f4cbc30ff193ff1e805","tid":528351,"uid":30836,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-13T16:40:25.000Z","msg":"呢個唔掂咪下一個"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-13T16:43:43.000Z","msg":"真係唔想放棄 我好難鐘意人<img src